OL,3,CCraig Bellamy announced as new Wales
OL,4,Cmanager to replace Rob Page
OL,6,FFormer footballer Craig Bellamy has
OL,7,Fbeen announced as the new Wales
OL,8,Fmanager.
OL,10,FThe The Football Association of Wales
OL,11,F(FAW) said it was "delighted to
OL,12,Fannounce the appointment of Craig
OL,13,FBellamy as the Cymru Men's National
OL,14,FTeam Head Coach until 2028".
OL,16,FBellamy will succeed Rob Page, who was
OL,17,Fsacked last month in the wake of
OL,18,Ffailing to qualify for Euro 2024,
OL,19,Fafter turning down the opportunity to
OL,20,Fstay at Burnley under new Clarets boss
OL,21,FScott Parker.
