OL,3,CCraig Bellamy announced as new Wales
OL,4,Cmanager to replace Rob Page
OL,6,FThe 44-year-old is a former Wales
OL,7,Fcaptain, who won 78 caps for his
OL,8,Fcountry between 1998 and 2013.
OL,10,FOther names who had previously been
OL,11,Flinked with the Wales manager position
OL,12,Fincluded former France forward Thierry
OL,13,FHenry and Georgia boss Willy Sagnol.
OL,15,FBut it is understood that Bellamy, who
OL,16,Fjust lost out on the job in 2017 when
OL,17,FRyan Giggs was appointed, impressed
OL,18,Fthe FAW hierarchy when he was
OL,19,Finterviewed in the north of England
OL,20,Flast week.
