OL,3,CCraig Bellamy announced as new Wales
OL,4,Cmanager to replace Rob Page
OL,6,FOn his appointment, Bellamy said:
OL,7,F"It's an incredible honour for me to
OL,8,Fbe given the opportunity to lead my
OL,9,Fcountry and it's the proudest moment
OL,10,Fof my career. It was always my
OL,11,Fultimate dream to become the Cymru
OL,12,FHead Coach and I am ready for the
OL,13,Fchallenge.
OL,15,F"I will give my full commitment to
OL,16,Fdevelop this team and I am passionate
OL,17,Fto bring continued success into Welsh
OL,18,Ffootball. I can't wait to get started
OL,19,Fwith our Nations League games in
OL,20,FSeptember."
