OL,3,CCraig Bellamy announced as new Wales
OL,4,Cmanager to replace Rob Page
OL,6,FThe FAW's Chief Football Officer, Dr.
OL,7,FDavid Adams, said: "I am absolutely
OL,8,Fdelighted to announce Craig as our new
OL,9,FHead Coach. We undertook a thorough
OL,10,Frecruitment process for the new Men's
OL,11,FNational Team Head Coach and Craig was
OL,12,Fidentified as the standout candidate.
OL,14,F"We are all looking forward to the
OL,15,FNations League games and working with
OL,16,FCraig to deliver success for Welsh
OL,17,FFootball."
