OL,3,CCraig Bellamy announced as new Wales
OL,4,Cmanager to replace Rob Page
OL,6,FOne thing Craig Bellamy will certainly
OL,7,Fbring to his new role as manager of
OL,8,FWales is plenty of passion and
OL,9,Fstraight-talking.
OL,11,FThe 44-year-old has never been one to
OL,12,Fmince his words and is unlikely to
OL,13,Fchange that tact now.
OL,15,FHis appointment will be a hit with
OL,16,Flarge portions of the fanbase but
OL,17,Fthose based in Swansea will take some
OL,18,Fconvincing. Cardiff born and bred,
OL,19,FBellamy never hid that his loyalties
OL,20,Flay in the capital.
