OL,3,CCraig Bellamy announced as new Wales
OL,4,Cmanager to replace Rob Page
OL,6,FLike any new manager, some good early
OL,7,Fresults will be important to galvanise
OL,8,Fthe entire fanbase behind him.
OL,10,FThere will also be concerns that
OL,11,FBellamy has never held a management
OL,12,Fjob at the top level. But those fears
OL,13,Fwill be allayed slightly given the
OL,14,Fexperience he has garnered working as
OL,15,Fan assistant to former Manchester City
OL,16,Fteam-mate Vincent Kompany at
OL,17,FAnderlecht and then Burnley. Though he
OL,18,Fwas overlooked by the Clarets for the
OL,19,Ftop job following Kompany's departure
OL,20,Fearlier this summer.
