OL,3,CCraig Bellamy announced as new Wales
OL,4,Cmanager to replace Rob Page
OL,6,FThe FAW will not have to explain to
OL,7,Fhim the significance of the Red Wall -
OL,8,Fthe most passionate section of Wales'
OL,9,Ffanbase - or the Welsh language. He
OL,10,Falready gets all of that.
OL,12,FBellamy's experience at the top level
OL,13,Fas a player is unquestionable, having
OL,14,Fplayed at major clubs like Manchester
OL,15,FCity, Liverpool and Newcastle.
OL,17,FHis lack of managerial experience
OL,18,Fmeans he enters the role with
OL,19,Fsomething to prove but, being a
OL,20,Fpassionate Welshman, this is a role he
OL,21,Fwill treat with the utmost respect.
